==English==
===Etymology===
{{prefix|en|xero|ophthalmia}}
===Noun===
{{en-noun|~}}
# {{lb|en|ophthalmology}} A condition due to a [[deficiency]] of vitamin A where the [[conjunctiva]] and [[cornea]] become [[dry]]. The condition starts with [[conjunctival]] [[xerosis]] and night [[blindness]] and progresses to corneal xerosis and, later, a severe condition called [[keratomalacia]].
#: {{syn|en|xerophthalmos|xerophthalmus}}
